                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120513-62-off350 t18120513-62-cd351"></join>, a silk handkerchief, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120513-62-victim679" type="victimName">
